#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------#
#
# Mouse, frame buttons and keyboard bindings
#
#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------#


# R - root window
# W - application window
# D - desktop application
# T - window title-bar
# S - window side, top, or bottom bar
# F - window frame (corners)
# I - icon window
# 2 - 0-9 title-bar buttons
# A - any context

# Root window menu shouldn't load
#       Button  Context Modif   Function
Mouse   0       R       A       Nop
Mouse   0       R       CS      Menu MenuFvwmRoot

# Button 1 in the title gives move or raise
#       Button  Context Modif   Function
Mouse   1       T       A       Move-or-Raise

#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Mouse windows buttons binding
# buttons: 1 3 5 7 9        0 8 6 4 2
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------

#       Button  Context Modif   Function
Mouse   0       2       A       Close
Mouse   1       2       A       Close
Mouse   2       2       A       Close
Mouse   0       4       A       Maximize 100 100

#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Now some keyboard shortcuts.
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Remove F1 help
Key     F1      R       A       -
